An update to the Counter-Strike: Source beta just been released. Steam will update itself automatically when you restart. Here is a list of the changes:<br/><br/><ul style="padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><b>COUNTER-STRIKE: SOURCE BETA CHANGES / ADDITIONS:</b><br/><li>Improved server changelevel behavior<br/><li>Improved behavior of full servers<br/><li>Improved "say" behavior on servers<br/><li>Addressed SetMode() issues<br/><li>Addressed "Invalid property: DT_BaseAnimating" issues<br/><li>Can now create windowed modes at the same size as the desktop<br/><li>Changed sv_pausable default to 0<br/><li>Improved command line parsing<br/><li>Improved change team binding<br/><li>Improved centerprint ID behavior<br/><li>Disallowed command "overview_mode" if not in observer mode<br/></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></ul><br/></p>
